<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>USAsurronshop</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #111;
      color: #fff;
    }

    header {
      background: #222;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header h1 {
      color: #facc15;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    nav {
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    nav a {
      margin: 0 15px;
      color: #facc15;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    section {
      padding: 40px 20px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    .card {
      background: #1e1e1e;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px #000;
    }

    .btn {
      background-color: #facc15;
      color: #000;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 1em;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    footer {
      background: #222;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>USAsurronshop</h1>
    <nav>
      <a href="#about">About</a>
      <a href="#bikes">Bikes</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section id="about" class="card">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>We specialize in high-performance Surron electric bikes for riders across the U.S. Whether you’re hitting the trails or the streets, we’ve got the perfect ride for you.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="bikes" class="card">
    <h2>Our Bikes</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Surron Light Bee X – Off-road beast</li>
      <li>Surron Storm Bee – Power meets style</li>
      <li>Custom Mods and Upgrades</li>
    </ul>
    <a href="#" class="btn">Shop Now</a>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="card">
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:usasurronshop@example.com">usasurronshop@example.com</a></p>
    <p>Instagram: @usasurronshop</p>
  </section>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 USAsurronshop. Built by Ekane Bright.
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
